<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>註冊頁面</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        input {
            width: 90%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        button {
            width: 95%;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: white;
            background-color: #28a745;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>註冊</h1>
        <form action="/register" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="用戶名稱" required>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="密碼" required>
            <button type="submit">註冊</button>
        </form>
        <p>已經有帳戶了？<a href="/login">登入</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>